<Link id="l00010" /><CodeLine lineNumber="10"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">/// It inserts ldtilecfg ahead of each group of tile registers. The algorithm</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00011" /><CodeLine lineNumber="11"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">/// walk each instruction of basic block in reverse order. All the tile</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00012" /><CodeLine lineNumber="12"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">/// registers that live out the basic block would be spilled and reloaded</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00013" /><CodeLine lineNumber="13"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">/// before its user. It also check the depenedency of the shape to ensure</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00014" /><CodeLine lineNumber="14"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">/// the shape is defined before ldtilecfg.</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00015" /><CodeLine lineNumber="15"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">//</span></CodeLine>
